" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180121%2F640_8a5db1800c5878dfd4b695becaf3551b.jpg&h=d3263ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180121/640_d2b606acf361de1092ff320edae99f35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180121%2F640_d2b606acf361de1092ff320edae99f35.jpg&h=76d3ec84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180121/640_f643bf8a2e4fbe92825a796cf9493e71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180121%2F640_f643bf8a2e4fbe92825a796cf9493e71.jpg&h=8ea08037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國歌手張木易2012年時爆出與12歲的混血女孩AKAMA MIKI相戀，2人經常在《微博》上高調放閃，女方還曾公開表示到16歲就要嫁給他，這段相差12歲的戀情讓許多人無法接受，更被挨轟有「戀童癖」，然而5年過去了，2人感情不受影響仍然甜蜜，更表示即將攜手步入禮堂。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《51新聞》指出，AKAMA MIKI的父母在她8歲時，請來張木易當音樂老師而相識。兩人在第一次時就對彼此一見鍾情，不時見面通信長達4年，等到Miki12歲的時候，才決定公開戀情，當時張木易率先在《微博》公開兩人親密照，接著Miki就在微博甜蜜互動，戀情曝光後讓不少人十分訝異。</strong><br />\n<br />\nAKAMA MIKI曾在《微博》表示等到16歲就嫁給張木易，但因為引來很多批評已經刪除留言。來自加拿大的AKAMA MIKI是中、日、德三國混血，曾參加新絲路中國少兒模特大賽獲得全國總決賽冠軍；張木易是香港國際星集團「北京世紀博灣」旗下的唱作藝人，因為藝人身分，這段被中國網友誇飾為「跨越一甲子」的戀情，也傳出有炒作之嫌。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180121/1282673/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180121%2F1282673%2F&d=NfLHfgbwHVIQMAjoJl73sjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7e110b97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180121%2F1282673%2F&h=c5e76f37\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180121/1282673/</a><br />\n<br />\n8歲mark到16歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一夠秤就劏豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一啲位都唔俾人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老味咁撚絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866e53b256e4abf6d441d2aa2b88948a12af8aa4","tid":536564,"uid":29880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T02:16:01.000Z","msg":"8歲mark到16歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1bedb2ecbf4005de12fff6637b03928c46d4b9","tid":536564,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70f3735abdc25ef53de24088a7c0ccc74e03c56a","tid":536564,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"更新：新增影片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180121/640_1a5278b3920ed62fede4730c6bc26c98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180121%2F640_1a5278b3920ed62fede4730c6bc26c98.jpg&h=b9b0d13f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180121/640_18d3f16e721d06c4399e0d8a41e71ef3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180121%2F640_18d3f16e721d06c4399e0d8a41e71ef3.jpg&h=8d8efd90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180121/640_bac3078942d3c056829efc1753247856.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180121%2F640_bac3078942d3c056829efc1753247856.jpg&h=69fd8d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180121/640_cd709bf65c7febbdf1b8906928db6f85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180121%2F640_cd709bf65c7febbdf1b890